{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<sub>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML <code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> 元素</strong>定义了一个文本区域，出于排版的原因，与主要的文本相比，应该展示得更低并且更小。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">内容分类 (en-US)</a></th>\n      <td>流式内容和短语内容</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的内容</th>\n      <td>短语内容</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">标签省略</th>\n      <td>不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的父元素</th>\n      <td>可以包含短语内容的任意元素</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">允许的 ARIA 角色</th>\n      <td>任意</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">DOM 接口</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个元素仅仅包含<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">全局属性 (en-US)</a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法注解","title":"用法注解","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>这个元素应该只用于排版目的，也就是改变文本的位置会改变含义，例如在数学中（<em>t2</em>，也可以考虑使用 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML (en-US)</a> 公式）或者化学符号（ <code>H2O</code>）。</li>\n  <li>这个元素不能用于样式上的目的，比如产品名称 LaTeX 的样式，这时应该使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a>样式： <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/vertical-align\"><code>vertical-align</code></a> 属性的 <code>sub</code> 值能实现相同效果。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>The chemical formula of water: H<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>sub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>sub</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>O<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果\">结果</h4>\n<p>The chemical formula of water: H2O</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-sub-and-sup-elements","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.sub"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a> HTML 元素会产生上标。要注意，你不能同时使用它们，你需要 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MathML (en-US)</a> 来同时产生化学符号旁边的下标和上标，代表它的序号和核子数。</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;msub&gt; (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;msup&gt; (en-US)</a>, 和 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">&lt;msubsup&gt; (en-US)</a> MathML 元素。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"用法注解","id":"用法注解"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"HTML <sub> 元素定义了一个文本区域，出于排版的原因，与主要的文本相比，应该展示得更低并且更小。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<sub>: The Subscript element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"sub","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<sub> : l'élément de mise en indice","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<sub>: 下付き文字要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<sub>: 아래 첨자 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/sub","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/sub/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub","title":"<sub>"}],"pageTitle":"<sub> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}